Cross Compiler generation and setup:


-Get crosstool to build the cross-compiler toolchain


sudo apt install build-essential git autoconf bison flex texinfo help2man gawk libtool-bin \libncurses5-dev unzip

git clone https://github.com/crosstool-ng/crosstool-ng

cd crosstool-ng/

git checkout crosstool-ng-1.26.0


-Generate configure script and files for crosstool


./bootstrap

./configure --enable-local    <---[configure crosstool to work locally rather than install it globally]

make


-Load CPU sample, Pi3 model b has a ARMV8 cortexA53 processor, in crosstool's samples: armv8-rpi3-linux-gnueabihf


./ct-ng __________            <---[place sample here(ex. arm-cortex_a8-linux-gnueabi), use ./ct-ng list-samples]

./ct-ng menuconfig

